# FormCoach — Feature Expansion with Lovable + ElevenLabs

Expand the existing FormCoach AI app with 5 new feature areas, leveraging **Lovable** for rapid UI/backend scaffolding and **ElevenLabs Conversational AI** for real-time voice coaching.

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Lovable["Lovable (React + Supabase)"]
        UI[Multi-Page React UI]
        DB[(Supabase DB)]
        Auth[Supabase Auth]
        Edge[Edge Functions]
    end

    subgraph Existing["Core Engine (keep as-is)"]
        MP[MediaPipe Pose]
        BIO[Biomechanics Engine]
        KC[Kinetic Chain Analysis]
        FP[Fatigue Predictor]
        BA[Bilateral Asymmetry]
    end

    subgraph ElevenLabs["ElevenLabs"]
        TTS[Text-to-Speech API]
        CONV[Conversational AI Agent]
        STT[Scribe STT]
    end

    UI --> MP
    MP --> BIO --> KC
    BIO --> FP
    BIO --> BA
    KC --> CONV
    FP --> CONV
    CONV --> TTS
    UI --> Auth
    UI --> DB
    Edge --> DB
```

---

## Platform Strategy

### Lovable — What It Provides

| Capability | How We Use It |
|---|---|
| **React + Tailwind code generation** | Build all new pages/screens via natural-language prompts |
| **Supabase integration** | User accounts, session history, check-in data, rehab plans |
| **GitHub two-way sync** | Connect to existing `younis-y/FormCoach` repo; all generated code syncs back |
| **One-click deploy** | Instant preview URLs for testing |
| **Lovable Cloud secrets** | Store ElevenLabs + Gemini API keys securely |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Lovable generates **React + Tailwind** code. The existing vanilla JS engine modules ([exercises.js](file:///Users/yo84/Desktop/Learning/Hackathon-FormCoach/src/exercises.js), [kineticChain.js](file:///Users/yo84/Desktop/Learning/Hackathon-FormCoach/src/kineticChain.js), etc.) will be wrapped as utility imports inside React components — they don't need rewriting.

### ElevenLabs — What It Provides

| Capability | How We Use It |
|---|---|
| **Conversational AI Agent** | Replace the existing one-way TTS with a **two-way real-time voice coach** that listens, understands context, and responds |
| **State-of-the-art turn-taking** | Natural conversation flow — the coach knows when you're mid-rep vs. asking a question |
| **Integrated RAG** | Feed biomechanical knowledge base into the agent for expert-level answers |
| **Client Tools (via SDK)** | The voice agent can trigger UI actions (start timer, log check-in, show exercise demo) |
| **@elevenlabs/client SDK** | Browser-side WebSocket/WebRTC connection for real-time voice |
| **Multilingual** | 32+ language support out of the box |

---

## Proposed Changes

### Feature 1: Live Coaching + Visual Form Detector + Real-Time Voice Advice

This upgrades the existing one-way voice TTS to a **two-way conversational AI coach** that can see your form data and talk back.

#### What changes

1. **Create an ElevenLabs Conversational AI Agent** (on elevenlabs.io dashboard)
   - System prompt: expert sports physiotherapist persona
   - Feed it the kinetic chain rules and biomechanical knowledge as RAG context
   - Define **client tools** the agent can call:
     - `getFormScore()` — returns current form score
     - `getCurrentAlerts()` — returns active form warnings
     - `getRootCause()` — returns kinetic chain root cause
     - `getFatigueData()` — returns fatigue curve prediction

2. **Replace [voice.js](file:///Users/yo84/Desktop/Learning/Hackathon-FormCoach/src/voice.js)** with a new `conversationalCoach.js` module
   - Uses `@elevenlabs/client` SDK to open a WebSocket to the Conversational AI agent
   - Continuously pushes form analysis data to the agent as context
   - Agent speaks proactively (form corrections) and responds to user questions
   - Falls back to existing TTS-only approach if no API key

3. **UI Enhancement** (via Lovable)
   - Voice interaction indicator (animated waveform when coach is speaking/listening)
   - "Ask Coach" button to initiate user questions
   - Microphone permission handling

#### [MODIFY] [voice.js](file:///Users/yo84/Desktop/Learning/Hackathon-FormCoach/src/voice.js)
Refactor into `conversationalCoach.js` — upgrade from one-way TTS to two-way Conversational AI using `@elevenlabs/client` SDK.

#### [NEW] `src/conversationalCoach.js`
New module wrapping ElevenLabs Conversational AI SDK with client tools that expose the biomechanics engine state.

---

### Feature 2: Daily 30-Second Check-In

A quick daily voice conversation where the coach asks how you feel and adjusts today's plan.

#### What changes

1. **Supabase table**: `check_ins` — stores daily responses (mood, soreness, energy, sleep)
2. **New page/screen**: `/check-in` — minimal UI that triggers a 30-second ElevenLabs conversation
3. **ElevenLabs Agent config**: A separate agent (or mode) focused on check-in questions:
   - "How are you feeling today?"
   - "Any soreness from yesterday?"
   - "Rate your energy 1-10"
4. **Client tools** the agent calls: `logCheckIn({ mood, soreness, energy })` → writes to Supabase
5. **Dashboard widget**: Trends over time (mood/soreness chart)

#### [NEW] `src/pages/CheckIn.tsx`
Full-screen check-in page with voice-first UI and animated avatar.

#### [NEW] `supabase/migrations/create_check_ins.sql`
`check_ins` table: `id`, `user_id`, `date`, `mood`, `soreness_areas`, `energy_level`, `sleep_quality`, `notes`.

---

### Feature 3: State-of-the-Art Biomechanical Knowledge

Make the coach deeply knowledgeable by feeding it a curated biomechanics knowledge base.

#### What changes

1. **Curate a knowledge base** of biomechanical principles:
   - Joint mechanics for each exercise (squat, push-up, deadlift, lunge, etc.)
   - Common movement faults and their root causes
   - Corrective exercise prescriptions
   - Mobility assessment protocols
2. **Upload to ElevenLabs RAG** — the Conversational AI agent can query this knowledge in real-time
3. **Expand [exercises.js](file:///Users/yo84/Desktop/Learning/Hackathon-FormCoach/src/exercises.js)** with additional exercises and more granular checks
4. **Knowledge surfacing in UI** — when the coach mentions a concept, show a card with the biomechanical explanation

#### [NEW] `knowledge/biomechanics.md`
Curated knowledge base document covering joint mechanics, movement faults, correctives.

#### [MODIFY] [exercises.js](file:///Users/yo84/Desktop/Learning/Hackathon-FormCoach/src/exercises.js)
Add new exercise definitions (deadlift, lunge, overhead press) with form checks.

---

### Feature 4: Rehab Transition Coach / Back-into-Exercise

Guide users returning from injury through progressive exercise programs.

#### What changes

1. **Supabase tables**:
   - `rehab_profiles` — injury type, recovery stage, limitations
   - `rehab_programs` — exercise progressions with week-by-week plans
2. **Onboarding flow** (Lovable page): User describes their injury/surgery through voice or form
3. **Adaptive coaching**: The ElevenLabs agent checks the user's rehab profile and:
   - Adjusts form thresholds (e.g., shallower squat depth for knee rehab)
   - Provides stage-appropriate encouragement
   - Flags if the user is pushing too hard too soon
4. **Progress tracking**: Weekly assessments stored in Supabase

#### [NEW] `src/pages/RehabOnboarding.tsx`
Multi-step onboarding flow for rehab users — voice-enabled.

#### [NEW] `src/components/RehabProgressTracker.tsx`
Visual progress through rehab phases with milestone markers.

#### [NEW] `supabase/migrations/create_rehab_tables.sql`
`rehab_profiles` and `rehab_programs` tables.

---

### Feature 5: Movement Snacks / Exercise Reminders

Push notifications and bite-sized exercise prompts throughout the day.

#### What changes

1. **Supabase table**: `movement_snacks` — library of 30-60 second exercises
2. **Notification system** (Lovable Edge Function + browser Push API):
   - User sets reminder schedule (e.g., every 2 hours during work)
   - Edge function triggers push notification
   - Clicking notification opens a quick movement snack screen
3. **Movement Snack screen**: Shows exercise with timer, optional voice coaching
4. **Streak tracking**: Gamification — how many days in a row you've completed your snacks

#### [NEW] `src/pages/MovementSnacks.tsx`
Browse and perform movement snacks with timer and voice guidance.

#### [NEW] `src/components/StreakTracker.tsx`
Gamified streak visualization.

#### [NEW] `supabase/migrations/create_snacks_tables.sql`
`movement_snacks` (library) and `user_snack_log` (completions) tables.

